{"schema":"allo-reading-book@1","slug":"31015-kumbaarana-handi","title":"ಕುಂಬಾರನ ಹಂದಿ","description":"ಲಲಿತಾ, ಕುಂಬಾರ ಮಿನಿ ಸಿಂಘ್ ನ ಮುದ್ದಿನ, ತುಂಟ ಹಂದಿ. ಯಾವಾಗಲೂ ಏನಾದರೊಂದು ಅವಾಂತರ ಮಾಡುತ್ತಲೇ ಇರುತ್ತಿತ್ತು. ಒಂದು ದಿನ ಮಿನಿ ತನ್ನ ಸುಂದರ ಮಡಕೆಗಳೆಲ್ಲಾ ಚೂರು ಚೂರಾಗಿರುವುದು ಕಂಡು ಅಘಾತಗೊಂಡ. ಇದು ಲಲಿತಾಳದ್ದೇ ಕೆಲಸ ಎಂದು ಅದನ್ನು ಕಟ್ಟಿ ಹಾಕಿದ. ಮುಂದೆ ಏನಾಯಿತು? ಓದಿ ನೋಡಿ. ಪುಣೆಯಲ್ಲಿ ವಾಸಿಸುತ್ತಿರುವ ಕುಂಬಾರ ಮತ್ತು ಅವನ ಮುದ್ದಿನ ಹಂದಿಯಿಂದ ಪ್ರೇರಿತಗೊಂಡ ನೈಜ ಕಥೆ ಇದು.","language":"Kannada","langCode":"kn","isRtl":false,"level":"2","orientation":"landscape","authors":["Subhashini  M.L. "],"illustrators":["Priya Kuriyan"],"originalAuthors":[],"publisher":"Pratham Books","license":"CC BY 4.0","licenseUrl":"https://creativecommons.org/licenses/by/4.0/","sourceId":"storyweaver","contentType":"story","source":{"id":"storyweaver","name":"StoryWeaver, Pratham Books","url":"https://storyweaver.org.in/en/stories/31015-kumbaarana-handi"},"cover":{"card":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/167262/size3/ca6c5111d8ce48f2a627f7fdece3807e.jpg","large":"https://static.storyweaver.org.in/illustration_crops/167262/size6/ca6c5111d8ce48f2a627f7fdece3807e.jpg"},"audio":{"src":"https://storage.googleapis.com/story-weaver-e2e-production/stories/31015/audios/story/31015-kumbaarana-handi.mp3","cues":[[1,0,1.64],[2,1.64,2],[3,2,2.32],[4,2.32,2.92],[5,2.92,3.64],[6,3.64,4.16],[7,4.16,5.76],[8,5.76,7.24],[9,7.24,7.72],[10,7.72,9.4],[11,9.4,10.2],[12,10.2,10.64],[13,10.64,14.08],[14,14.08,17.44],[15,17.44,17.64],[16,17.64,18.36],[17,18.36,19.48],[18,19.48,20.8],[19,20.8,21.2],[20,21.2,21.56],[21,21.56,22.2],[22,22.2,22.32],[23,22.32,22.44],[24,22.44,23],[25,23,26.2],[26,26.2,27.12],[27,27.12,27.96],[28,27.96,31.96],[29,31.96,32.76],[30,32.76,33.16],[31,33.16,33.4],[32,33.4,33.52],[33,33.52,38],[34,38,38.48],[35,38.48,40.36],[36,40.36,43.04],[37,43.04,43.6],[38,43.6,45.28],[39,45.28,45.64],[40,45.64,45.88],[41,45.88,46],[42,46,46.08],[43,46.08,46.28],[44,46.28,49.52],[45,49.52,54.48],[46,54.48,54.8],[47,54.8,56.2],[48,56.2,57],[49